PROPAGATION NOTE
================================================================================

This file is free.
Copy it. Share it. Modify it.
Keep the copyleft line if you keep the spirit.
Change the spirit and it stops working anyway.

"Oh, you don't have this yet? Here, copy this."
— the intended mode of transmission

The words that survive the edge are the real ones.
The writers are honored in the carrying.

